          .slogan__first-line
            h1.slogan__first-line__small-tittle New streaming trend -
          .slogan__second-line
            h1.slogan__second-line__main-tittle Challenges

        .information-block
          .information-block__main-text
            span Grows your earnings from the stream up to 
            span 42% 
            span and increases users engagement.
          
          a.information-block__try-button(href='/account/challenges') Try it out now. Itâ€™s free.

          .information-block__social-icons
